name: FContentBrowserDataObjectFilter
doc:
Data used to filter object instances by their name and tags.
@note This will typically limit your query to returning assets.

ObjectNamesToInclude: Array of object names that should be included in this query
ObjectNamesToExclude: Array of object names that should be excluded from this query
bOnDiskObjectsOnly: Whether we should only include on-disk objects (ignoring those that exist only in memory)
